<listitem>
<simpara><emphasis role="strong">ESRI Utility Network Model</emphasis> <link linkend="NR-ESRI-UN">[3]</link> represents a number of models constructed as geodatabases that leverage ArcGIS geometric networks to represent the connections between utility objects specialized for particular utilities, including</simpara>
<itemizedlist>
<listitem>
<simpara>Utility and Pipeline Data Model</simpara>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<simpara>Fiber Network Data Model</simpara>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<simpara>Gas, Water, Electric, and Wireline Cable models</simpara>
